snippet: Serena Williams underlined the difference in class and power between her and the rest of the women's field with a 6-0 6-4 demolition of fourth seed Agnieszka Radwanska on Thursday to reach her seventh Australian Open final....
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams underlined the difference in class and power between her and the rest of the women's field with a 6-0 6-4 demolition of fourth seed Agnieszka Radwanska on Thursday to reach her seventh Australian Open final.

headline.print_headline: Serena Demolishes Radwanska to Make Final in Australia
headline.main: Serena Demolishes Radwanska to Make Final in Australia
